	abstract = {BACKGROUND AND STUDY AIMS: Artificial intelligence based computer-aided polyp detection (CADe) systems receive regular updates and occasionally offer customizable detection thresholds which impact their performance, but little is known about these effects. This study aimed to compare the performance of different CADe systems on the same benchmark dataset.
